subject: Good morning to you son of
body:
Good morning to you son of God!
Today is the day to start something new, try something different or have fun in God! May today be full of beautiful moments that make you feel blessed. Wishing you a happy Sunday!Amen

subject: Re:    Good morning to you son of
body:
Good morning to you too! I hope you're having a wonderful Sunday. It's always exciting to start something new or try something different, isn't it? What kind of new things are you planning on trying today?

Best wishes,
Elyse
